data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Paradise! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath house is the epitome of Florida living, offering an abundance of features and amenities that will make you feel right at home and on vacation at the same time.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the high ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere throughout the house. The tile floors, not only beautiful but easy to maintain, flow seamlessly from room to room.  The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, complete with an eat-in bar space that's perfect for casual dining or entertaining guests. Two large pantries provide ample storage for all your kitchen essentials. The kitchen also boasts newer appliances, ensuring your culinary adventures are a breeze. The split floor plan offers privacy from the luxurious master suite that takes up the whole right side of the house. With French doors that open up onto the lanai, it's a wonderful way to start and end your day! This home also features a spacious office/den with fantastic windows to let in the sunshine as you work or play.  For eco-conscious homeowners, this property offers the convenience of an electric vehicle charger in the 2-car garage, making it easy to keep your EV charged and ready to go.  One of the standout features of this home is the BRAND NEW roof, providing peace of mind and years of worry-free living. This house also has hurricane shutters for further protection.  Step outside to your own private oasis. The solar-heated saltwater pool is perfect for year-round enjoyment, and the oversized lot ensures plenty of space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Surrounding the pool area are fruit trees and lush plants, offering a taste of Florida's bounty right in your backyard. Plus, there's plenty of room to add a garden in the spacious backyard, allowing you to cultivate your own fresh produce and create a beautiful outdoor retreat.  Worried about keeping your landscaping in top shape? Fear not, as the property comes equipped with an irrigation system powered by a well, helping you maintain your outdoor paradise with ease.  Located near the pristine beaches of Englewood and Venice with numerous options for outdoor activities such as kayaking, fishing, boating and beaching, great shopping, restaurants, and even spring training ball fields, this home is perfectly situated for the ultimate Florida lifestyle. Seller is providing a HOME WARRANTY for one year as well!  Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in a prime location. Schedule your showing today and make this beautiful house your forever home!
